name: fanton 001
description:
I started playing my first instrument when I was 5 years old. I always liked to make instrument sounds with my voice, but I had never been able to write lyrics. This is the first and only song that I've managed to write and I decided I should share it!!!

I was privileged to have the cover designed by the wonderful @drielemart and animated by the excellent @PlayManNF.

Enjoy!
